{"id":156958,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/cover-story－麻辣誘惑-年營收4億人民幣/","date":"2011-05-31T23:30:42Z","modified":"2011-12-28T23:42:26Z","title":"Cover Story－麻辣誘惑 年營收4億人民幣","content":"<p>喜歡吃麻辣鍋的台灣消費者，一定聽過鼎王，每到吃飯時間，鼎王的店門口總是排著滿滿的人潮，就連宵夜時間，門口還是有一群來朝聖的饕客。分布於上海、北京、天津的麻辣誘惑也有著如此的吸引力，讓每天有超過1萬2000人次的消費者，到麻辣誘惑的17家店解饞，麻辣誘惑也創造出一年超過4億元（人民幣，下同）的龐大營收。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://chinatimes.feedsportal.com/c/33012/f/537211/s/15742cd2/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=Cover+Story%EF%BC%8D%E9%BA%BB%E8%BE%A3%E8%AA%98%E6%83%91+%E5%B9%B4%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B64%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.chinatimes.com%2Fmainland%2F11050504%2F112011053100215.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=Cover+Story%EF%BC%8D%E9%BA%BB%E8%BE%A3%E8%AA%98%E6%83%91+%E5%B9%B4%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B64%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.chinatimes.com%2Fmainland%2F11050504%2F112011053100215.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101095270625/u/0/f/537211/c/33012/s/15742cd2/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101095270625/u/0/f/537211/c/33012/s/15742cd2/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinatimes.feedsportal.com/c/33012/f/537211/s/15742cd2/mf.gif\" /></p>\n<p>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> </p>\n<p>\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[18424],"tags":[16304,15396]}